data.name: lblIntro.Text
data.value:
Welcome to AutoBright version Beta 2.3!
Please note that not all monitors support AutoBright, so you may experience unexpected behaviour or crashes. You can try looking for a setting in your display's settings for DDC and ensuring that it is enabled, but this may not be present, or may not fix the problem anyway.
In order to fetch times for sunrise and sunset, you need to enter a location in the form of latitude and longitude coordinates. These coordinates are handled by an external 3rd party API, so I am not responsible for any data you enter.
Fetching these times does require an internet connection, so if a connection is not found, or some other error occurs, the most recently saved times will be used instead. You will be notified if this happens.
Press continue to detect screen configuration and current brightness settings.
